OL,3,CAs Delhi chokes after Diwali, India
OL,4,Ctrials artificial rain to clear
OL,5,Cpollution
OL,7,FThe city's government has approved a
OL,8,Fcloud-seeding operation between
OL,9,FOctober 28 and 30, the first such
OL,10,Fexperiment in the Indian capital,
OL,11,Fhoping that induced rainfall will help
OL,12,Fwash away the thick smog that blankets
OL,13,Fthe city every winter.
OL,15,FThe operation follows the Hindu
OL,16,Ffestival of Diwali, which marks the
OL,17,Fonset of the pollution season in
OL,18,Fnorthern India.
