OL,7,FAlthough authorities permitted only
OL,8,F"green" fireworks until 10pm on Diwali
OL,9,Fnight, residents across the capital
OL,10,Fcontinued bursting traditional
OL,11,Ffirecrackers late into the night,
OL,12,Ffilling the air with dense smoke.
OL,14,FCombined with emissions from vehicles,
OL,15,Findustrial activity, and widespread
OL,16,Fstubble burning in neighbouring Punjab
OL,17,Fand Haryana, the post-Diwali haze
OL,18,Fpushed Delhi's Air Quality Index (AQI)
OL,19,Finto the "severe" category.
