OL,7,FCloud seeding involves an aircraft
OL,8,Freleasing a mix of silver iodide,
OL,9,Fiodised salt, and rock salt into
OL,10,Fmoisture-rich clouds above the city.
OL,11,FThe particles act as seeds for
OL,12,Fraindrops, triggering rainfall that
OL,13,Fmay wash down dangerous pollutants
OL,14,Ffrom the atmosphere.
OL,16,FThe technique is used in several hot
OL,17,Fand arid climates, including in the
OL,18,FUAE and some states in the US, such as
OL,19,FTexas.
