OL,12,FDelhi's First Minister Rekha Gupta
OL,13,Fsaid all technical preparations for
OL,14,Fthe cloud-seeding operation have been
OL,15,Fcompleted.
OL,17,F"This initiative will help settle
OL,18,Fairborne pollutants and bring
OL,19,Ftemporary relief," she said, calling
OL,20,Fit a milestone in Delhi's evolving
OL,21,Fenvironmental management strategy.
