OL,7,FLocal Environment Minister Manjinder
OL,8,FSingh Sirsa added that aircraft
OL,9,Fequipped with dispersal systems will
OL,10,Frelease silver iodide and sodium
OL,11,Fchloride particles into moisture-laden
OL,12,Fclouds, in coordination with
OL,13,Fscientists from the Indian Institute
OL,14,Fof Technology (IIT) Kanpur and the
OL,15,FIndia Meteorological Department.
