OL,7,FOfficials said the project follows
OL,8,Fmonths of feasibility studies and
OL,9,Fsimulation trials. If successful,
OL,10,FDelhi's experiment could become a
OL,11,Fmodel for other Indian cities
OL,12,Fgrappling with seasonal pollution
OL,13,Fcrises.
OL,15,FAlongside the artificial rain effort,
OL,16,Fthe government has reintroduced
OL,17,Fvehicle restrictions, intensified dust-
OL,18,Fcontrol measures, and expanded green
OL,19,Fbuffers to manage air quality through
OL,20,Fthe winter months.
